if os.path.exists('out'):
    shutil.rmtree('out')
response = session.post('/upload-files', files=[('images', ('one.jpg', open
    ('static/pexels-photo-126407.jpeg', 'rb'), 'image/jpeg')), ('images', (
    'two.jpg', open('static/pexels-photo-923360.jpeg', 'rb'), 'image/jpeg'))])
ensure_success(response)
assert_files_equals(f'./out/one.jpg', 'static/pexels-photo-126407.jpeg')
assert_files_equals(f'./out/two.jpg', 'static/pexels-photo-923360.jpeg')
